# Candle Master - Environment Variables Example
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your actual API keys

# AI Chatbot Configuration
# Choose ONE of the following:

# Option 1: Claude AI (Anthropic)
# Get your API key from: https://console.anthropic.com/
VITE_CLAUDE_API_KEY=your_claude_api_key_here

# Option 2: Gemini AI (Google)
# Get your API key from: https://ai.google.dev/
VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# Note: Only one AI service is needed. Choose based on:
# - Claude: Better at nuanced conversations, great for education
# - Gemini: Fast responses, good for quick answers

# Security Notes:
# 1. Never commit .env to Git (it's in .gitignore)
# 2. Keep API keys secret
# 3. Rotate keys regularly
# 4. Consider using a backend proxy in production
